  "body": "Separated from https://github.com/fluent/fluentd/pull/468\n\nIt looks TimeSlicedOutput does not push chunks to queues until specified time comes. No chunk is pushed, then no chunk is flushed. \n\nhttps://github.com/fluent/fluentd/blob/a5d489b2123faf69b156b58602990ae040dc8161/lib/fluent/output.rb#L526-L531\n\n``` ruby\n          nowslice = @time_slicer.call(Engine.now.to_i - @time_slice_wait)\n          @buffer.keys.each {|key|\n            if key < nowslice\n              @buffer.push(key)\n            end\n          }\n```\n\nVoices from users\n- https://twitter.com/fd0/status/165995569834242049\n- http://blog.kyanny.me/entry/2012/02/09/002430\n",
